    <p>During my time at <a href="https://www.ua.edu.ph/academics/degrees-and-programs/" target="_blank">the University of the Assumption</a>, I immersed myself in coding, building projects, and mastering the fundamentals of web development. Every challenge, from debugging to optimizing performance, pushed me to improve my problem-solving skills. After graduation, I've been applying my knowledge to real-world projects, refining my skills in front-end and back-end development. I continue to learn new In the future, I aspire to work on innovative web solutions that impact users globally. Whether it's leading development teams, launching my own projects, or contributing to open-source communities, I aim to keep growing and pushing the boundaries of what's possible in web development.</p>

